snippet.title: The Sims 4 Jungle Adventure: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
"Take your Sims on a mysterious adventure into the wild and discover a new culture with The Sims™ 4 Jungle Adventure*.
 
 Available February 27th for PC and Mac.
 
 Learn more about this Game Pack: http://x.ea.com/44816
 
 Explore a unique wilderness landscape, revealing a temple, jungle obstacles, cursed relics, and treasures. Experience the culture and customs of Selvadorada, from devouring local eats to learning spicy dance moves!

CREDIT 
“Todo Cambio”
Performed by Becky G
Used courtesy of Kemosabe Records/RCA Records 
By arrangement with Sony Music Entertainment
 
LINKS 
Becky G's “Todo Cambio” is available now: 
Spotify: http://smarturl.it/BGTodoCambioSp 
 
Follow Becky G! Official Site: http://iambeckyg.com 


 
 *REQUIRES THE SIMS 4 GAME (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES TO PLAY. SEE www.thesims.com/system-requirements for MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR THIS PACK."
